      "content": "but that’s the thing, it’s not like anyone left but me. i failed so publicly that there’s no way to rebuild. the \"me\" that people respected is just gone, like it never existed. how am i supposed to just \"make small changes\" when the person who was supposed to make those changes doesn't even exist anymore? it feels like a hollow shell.",
